Sonic::ManagedStorage::Audio::TrackTags

Sonic::ManagedStorage::Audio::TrackTags Struct Reference

Detailed Description

Struct specifying file tags for audio extraction.

Tag information that may be included when extracting CD-audio to a file format that supports such data (Mp3, etc.)
